SubjectBy-elections (3) - Calgary Centre - Durham - Victoria
PrecisOrder directing that WRITS OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancies in the House of Commons for the electoral districts of CALGARY CENTRE (Alberta), DURHAM (Ontario), and VICTORIA (British-Columbia), with polling to take place on November 26, 2012.
